> """
> Vértice Platform - Centralized Enumerations
> ============================================
  
> This module contains all enumerated types used across the Vértice cybersecurity platform.
> Enums provide type-safe, validated constants with string representations for APIs and UIs.
  
> Features:
>     - Type-safe enum classes extending str and Enum
>     - JSON-serializable string values
>     - IDE autocomplete support
>     - Validation for API inputs
>     - MITRE ATT&CK framework alignment
>     - OWASP security standards compliance
  
> Usage:
>     >>> from shared.enums import ThreatLevel, ServiceStatus
>     >>> if threat.level == ThreatLevel.CRITICAL:
>     >>>     alert_soc()
>     >>>
>     >>> status = ServiceStatus.HEALTHY
>     >>> assert status.value == "healthy"
  
> Author: Vértice Platform Team
> License: Proprietary
> """
  
! from enum import Enum
  
